<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0217a" xml:id="I01.0080.0217a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0217a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 80</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0217a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>郭顯邕等造一切經記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0217a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0217a0101">大唯那
<lb ed="I" n="0217a02" type="honorific"/>大唯那
<lb ed="I" n="0217a03" type="honorific"/>大唯那
<lb ed="I" n="0217a04" type="honorific"/>大唯那</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0217b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0217b0101">夫真宗沖玄。法理難尋。空湛幽<note n="0217001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31035"/>＝廓【史】</note><note n="0217001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31035"/>【佛拓】，廓【史】</note><app n="0217001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廓</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31035"/></rdg></app>。遠而莫□。自非神智通感。安能曉<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">監</unclear>往
<lb ed="I" n="0217b02" type="honorific"/>述。慧化津流。非文無以傳於萬古。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">契</unclear>藏之徒。必藉聲教以啓寤。上第名儒。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b03" type="honorific"/>亦因言說以<note n="0217002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30304"/>＝詮【史】</note><note n="0217002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30304"/>【佛拓】，詮【史】</note><app n="0217002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30304"/></rdg></app>厥義。其有王子。名曰悉達。奉花定光。託陰摩耶。棄彼萬<note n="0217003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31036"/>＝邦【史】</note><note n="0217003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31036"/>【佛拓】，邦【史】</note><app n="0217003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31036"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b04" type="honorific"/>不以為珍。盜踰宮闕。軒駕道樹。是以法鼓一擊。則塵沙玉潤。等慈宣暢。隨
<lb ed="I" n="0217b05" type="honorific"/>□□受。三車之教既周。便尒西謝。輟響靈山。埋光兩樹。斷句韜章。長<note n="0217004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02793"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0217004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02793"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0217004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app>息
<lb ed="I" n="0217b06" type="honorific"/>照。於是寶船頃壞。法摧□而莫舉。凝神虛寂。飛聲東夏。夢感漢庭。弘興<note n="0217005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31037"/>＝再【史】</note><note n="0217005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31037"/>【佛拓】，再【史】</note><app n="0217005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">再</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31037"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0217b07" type="honorific"/>序。金容雖隱。慧音永盛。風<note n="0217006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB12017"/>＝軌【史】</note><note n="0217006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB12017"/>【佛拓】，軌【史】</note><app n="0217006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB12017"/></rdg></app>慧日。迄今不絕。然此大邑主練行。沙門悲教
<lb ed="I" n="0217b08" type="honorific"/>二禪師。識度清高。解佩緇門。少投道服。志業无為。<note n="0217007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30602"/>＝整【史】</note><note n="0217007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30602"/>【佛拓】，整【史】</note><app n="0217007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">整</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30602"/></rdg></app>三千而不減。攝六賊
<lb ed="I" n="0217b09" type="honorific"/>於四禪。秉榮自護。愛惜浮囊。處泥不汙。粲若明珠。復能勸率迷俗。以<note n="0217008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31038"/>＝示【史】</note><note n="0217008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31038"/>【佛拓】，示【史】</note><app n="0217008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">示</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31038"/></rdg></app>未
<lb ed="I" n="0217b10" type="honorific"/>悟。次有大經主中丘縣人郭顯邕。可謂樹靈根於九泉。孤條鬱嶷如獨穎。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b11" type="honorific"/>出自太原。因封關左。上祖郭溫。青冀二州刺史。邕其後也。斯人雖形居塵
<lb ed="I" n="0217b12" type="honorific"/>境。心栖方外。知炎宅非久之資。睹危城同于并葛。遂共禪師等。契信內融。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b13" type="honorific"/>崇茲勝福。道素競湊。五百餘人皆是一<app type="star" corresp="#0217003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31036"/></rdg></app>豪<note n="0217009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">桀＝傑【史】</note><note n="0217009" resp="ihp" type="mod">桀【佛拓】，傑【史】</note><app n="0217009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">傑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">桀</rdg></app>。邑里頂最。給孤之徒。脫纓
<lb ed="I" n="0217b14" type="honorific"/>之侶。建此高節。同<note n="0217010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30896"/>＝規【史】</note><note n="0217010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30896"/>【佛拓】，規【史】</note><app n="0217010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30896"/></rdg></app>妙果。於是競捨己財。頃寶弗□。敬造一切經卷。過三
<lb ed="I" n="0217b15" type="honorific"/>千部□十二。磬竭盡章。不漏巧遺建。祈蠰佉之早遇。泣娑羅之難追。願度
<lb ed="I" n="0217b16" type="honorific"/>生死流。俱時昇彼岸。功就悠駕。刊銘金石。徽音遐代。千載不易。　頌曰
<lb ed="I" n="0217b17" type="honorific"/>靈覺闡朗。慧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">日</unclear>獨曉。眉如初月。含暉皎皎。敷揚四諦。悟果億兆。一坐說法。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b18" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">刦</unclear>逕十<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">介</unclear>。人天蒙賴。得道不少。<note n="0217011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00450"/>＝雙【史】</note><note n="0217011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00450"/>【佛拓】，雙【史】</note><app n="0217011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB00450"/></rdg></app>林變白。現<note n="0217012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31040"/>＝瑞【史】</note><note n="0217012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31040"/>【佛拓】，瑞【史】</note><app n="0217012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑞</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31040"/></rdg></app>光表。大眾恒沙。<note n="0217013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31041"/>＝憂【史】</note><note n="0217013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31041"/>【佛拓】，憂【史】</note><app n="0217013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">憂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31041"/></rdg></app>心悄悄。
<lb ed="I" n="0217b19" type="honorific"/>澄神空寂。金容<note n="0217014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31039"/>＝皎【史】</note><note n="0217014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31039"/>【佛拓】，皎【史】</note><app n="0217014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31039"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0217014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31039"/></rdg></app>。埋光綴照。哀哉長了。<note place="inline">其一</note>積行累德。道備成功。半偈碎
<lb ed="I" n="0217b20" type="honorific"/>身。天帝改<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">容</unclear>。位超十住。人中之龍。馳軀西域。一去不東。瓊山崩頹。遺教許
<lb ed="I" n="0217b21" type="honorific"/>宗。聖言不墜。千稔傳通。<note place="inline">其二</note>新經巨嶽。寶聚巍巍。造化始有。世帝奇希。往<note n="0217015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30136"/>＝昔【史】</note><note n="0217015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30136"/>【佛拓】，昔【史】</note><app n="0217015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30136"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0217b22" type="honorific"/>舍城。今日何期。諸天讚嘆。散華霏霏。魔王奉獻。尼乾歸依。化感寰外。上及
<lb ed="I" n="0217b23" type="honorific"/>紫微。上矚斯福。見性不疑。<note place="inline">其三</note>神州沃壤。誕生漢賢。存心聖教。重法輕珍。邑
<lb ed="I" n="0217b24" type="honorific"/>人五百。助德靈仙。雲奔力<note n="0217016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB15137"/>＝競【史】</note><note n="0217016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB15137"/>【佛拓】，競【史】</note><app n="0217016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB15137"/></rdg></app>。剋就不年。芳延宇宙。振響六天。闡提逢遇。宿
<lb ed="I" n="0217b25" type="honorific"/>殖有緣。羅王登道。地獄生蓮。含形獲慶。拔苦忘纏。刊石雕文。永劫不遷。<note place="inline">其四</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0217b26" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　大齊天統元年歲次大梁九月庚辰朔六日乙酉</p>
